<h3>Bibliography</h3>

<p class="bibl">Bromhead, H. W. "An Illustrator of Blake." <span class="book">Art Journal</span>. Vol. 62 (1900). Internet Archive</span>. 237-39. Contributed by the Getty Research Institute. Web. 7 August 2020.</p>


<p class="bibl">Galchinsky, Michael. "Levetus [née Moss], Celia (c. 1819–1873), writer." <span class="book">Oxford Dictionary of National Biography</span>. Web. 7 August 2020. (Note: this entry concerns another Celia Levetus (née Moss). Celia Anna Levetus is only mentioned at the end, in useful advice about distinguishing between the two. They are not said to have been related.</p>
 


